sourcesContent:
<nz-page-header [nzGhost]="false" nzBackIcon [nzTitle]="'cancelReason.title' | translate"
  [nzSubtitle]="'cancelReason.subtitle' | translate">
</nz-page-header>
<nz-card [nzActions]="[tmplActions]" style="mt-16">
  <form nz-form [formGroup]="form" (ngSubmit)="onSubmit()">
    <input formControlName="id" type="hidden" hidden>
    <nz-form-item>
      <nz-form-label nzRequired nzFor="title">{{ 'profile.title' | translate }}</nz-form-label>
      <nz-form-control [nzErrorTip]="'error.titleInvalid' | translate">
        <input nz-input formControlName="title" id="title" />
      </nz-form-control>
    </nz-form-item>
    <nz-form-item>
      <nz-form-label nzFor="userType">User Type</nz-form-label>
      <nz-form-control>
        <nz-select nzMode="default" nzPlaceHolder="Please select" formControlName="userType">
          <nz-option nzLabel="Driver" nzValue="Driver"></nz-option>
          <nz-option nzLabel="Rider" nzValue="Rider"></nz-option>
        </nz-select>
      </nz-form-control>
    </nz-form-item>
    <nz-form-item>
      <nz-form-label nzRequired nzFor="isEnabled">{{ 'profile.visibilityStatus' | translate }}</nz-form-label>
      <nz-form-control>
        <nz-switch required id="isEnabled" formControlName="isEnabled"></nz-switch>
      </nz-form-control>
    </nz-form-item>
    <ng-template #tmplActions>
      <button nz-button nzType="primary" [disabled]="form.invalid" (click)="onSubmit()">{{'profile.submit' |
        translate}}</button>
    </ng-template>
  </form>
</nz-card>
